| Category | Score | Notes |
|----------|-------|-------|
| **Documentation** | 🟢 A | SPECS.md at every level, JSDoc on all services, CHANGELOG maintained |
| **Code Structure** | 🟢 A | Feature-sliced frontend, service-layer backend, clear separation |
| **Type Safety** | 🟡 B | Frontend is TypeScript, backend is JavaScript (no types) |
| **Error Handling** | 🟢 A | Try/catch everywhere, non-fatal steps for rollup/reports, ingestion logs |
