| **Test Coverage** | 🔴 F | **Zero automated tests** — no test framework, no test files |
| **Code Debt** | 🟢 A | No TODOs, no HACKs, no commented-out code |
| **Dead Code** | 🟢 A | `multer` in package.json is unused (only busboy is used), otherwise clean |

