## 4. Architecture Review

### Backend (Express + Mongoose)

```
POST /webhook (OPEN)
├── csvParserService.parseCSV()
├── dealerGroupDetector.resolveDealerBatch()
├── dealerMetricsIngestionService.ingestDealerMetricsCSV()
│   ├── DailyDealerSnapshot.bulkWrite() [batch 500]
│   ├── rollupService.rebuildRollupsForDate()
│   └── reportService.runPostIngestionReports()
└── FileIngestionLog (audit trail)

GET /analytics/* (JWT PROTECTED)
├── /overview — high-level stats
├── /groups — dealer groups with aggregated summaries
├── /groups/:slug/locations — locations within a group
├── /groups/:slug/monthly — monthly rollups
├── /dealers/small — paginated dealer list (server-side sort)
├── /dealers/:id/trend — daily trend snapshots
├── /dealers/:id/monthly — dealer monthly rollups
└── /budget/* — budget data by state/rep

POST /auth/* (MIXED)
├── /login — open
├── /accept-invite — open
├── /me — protected
├── /change-password — protected
├── /invite — admin+
├── /users — admin+
└── DELETE /users/:id — admin+ (role-scoped)

POST /reports/* (JWT PROTECTED, admin+)
├── /recipients — manage email recipients
├── /daily-digest — manual trigger
├── /health-check — manual trigger
└── /preview/daily-digest — HTML preview
```

### Frontend (React 19 + Vite 8)

```
App.tsx
├── AuthProvider (context)
├── /login → LoginPage
├── /invite → AcceptInvitePage
└── /* → ProtectedRoute → Dashboard
    ├── AppShell (header, settings, digest buttons)
    ├── TabBar (Groups / Dealers / All)
    ├── FilterBar (Rep, State, Status, Activity Mode)
    └── DealerTable (32KB — largest component)
        ├── GroupRows (expandable, lazy-loaded locations)
        ├── DealerRows (infinite scroll, server-side pagination)
        ├── Multi-column sort with remove
        ├── Heatmap-colored cells
        └── Skeleton shimmer loading
```

### Potential Architecture Concerns

| Concern | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **N+1 query in group locations** | `GET /groups/:slug/locations` does `Promise.all(locations.map(loc => findOne snapshot))` — one DB query per location. For a 77-location group like Blue Compass RV, that's 77 sequential queries. Should use `$lookup` aggregation or a batch query. |
| **Full group fetch on every filter change** | `DealerGroup.find({}).lean()` loads ALL groups (potentially hundreds) on every `/analytics/groups` call, then filters in pipeline. Could use `$match` to filter groups server-side. |
| **Serverless cold start risk** | 60-second `maxDuration` in `vercel.json` is generous. The 13-second ingestion time is fine, but heavy aggregation queries on cold starts may approach limits. |
| **Single-file analytics route** | `routes/analytics/index.js` is **784 lines** — a monolith. Should be split into sub-modules (groups, dealers, overview). |
| **DealerTable component** | At **32KB / 800+ lines**, this is a complex monolith. Should be decomposed into GroupTable and DealerTable sub-components. |

